# React Frontend Template Rules (templates/react-frontend/)

**Repository**: idp-templates  
**Inherits from**: `/idp-templates/.cursorrules` (root)

## Overview
Backstage template for scaffolding React single-page applications with modern tooling, nginx deployment, and CI/CD pipeline.

## Template Purpose
- Generate React SPA with Vite
- TypeScript support
- Component library structure
- nginx production deployment
- Environment configuration

## Template Variables
```yaml
${{ values.name }}              # App name
${{ values.description }}       # Description
${{ values.owner }}             # Owner
${{ values.api_url }}           # Backend API URL
${{ values.include_router }}    # Include React Router
```

## Generated Structure
- Vite + React + TypeScript
- Component folder structure
- nginx.conf for production
- Multi-stage Dockerfile
- Environment variable injection
- Jest/Vitest testing setup

